				I got this weapon tonight on the Brell server (thank Gnarg, Quall and Xazm for helping!). <BR>
<BR>
Let me tell you, for the difficulty of this shadow knight, this weapon is not worth it.<BR>
<BR>
First off, it's heavy.  Second off, it's no drop.  Then add to that the fact that it's values are low for the level of the mob and that the effect is only level one.<BR>
<BR>
You're better off going with a Langseax of the Wolves, BiBs, GZ or even an Avenger Battle Axe.
